    "/webhooks/documentation": {
      "get": {
        "operationId": "v1.webhooks.documentation",
        "description": "Complete documentation for configuring and receiving webhooks from Supernova.\n\nWEBHOOK SECRET\n===============\nUse this secret to verify incoming webhook signatures.\nAvailable in your merchant credentials in the dashboard.\n⚠️ NEVER share this secret with anyone. Keep it secure on your server.\n\nSIGNATURE VERIFICATION\n======================\nAlgorithm: HMAC-SHA256\nHeader: X-Webhook-Signature\n\nVerification Steps:\n1. Extract the X-Webhook-Signature header from the incoming request\n2. Get the raw request body as a string\n3. Compute HMAC-SHA256 hash of the request body using your webhook_secret\n4. Compare the computed hash with the received signature using timing-safe comparison\n5. If they match, the webhook is authentic and has not been tampered with\n\nWhy Verify?\nVerifying signatures ensures the webhook really came from Supernova and the payload\nhas not been modified in transit. This prevents malicious actors from sending fake events.\n\nWEBHOOK HEADERS\n================\n**Content-Type:** application/json\n\n**X-Webhook-Signature:** HMAC-SHA256 signature of the raw request body\n\n**X-Webhook-Timestamp:** Unix timestamp when the event occurred\n\n**X-Webhook-Event:** Event type (e.g., transaction.approved)\n\n**X-Webhook-ID:** Unique identifier for the webhook event (starts with \"evt_\")",
        "summary": "Get Webhook Documentation",
        "tags": [
          "Webhooks",
          "Webhook"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "event": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "transaction.approved"
                    },
                    "event_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "evt_c244fb7f09b67dc0936ff5798232b5f3"
                    },
                    "timestamp": {
                      "type": "integer",
                      "const": 1771710493
                    },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "id": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "const": 6
                        },
                        "internal_reference": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "TXN-XXDIZYK7-DBBC4D"
                        },
                        "merchant_reference": {
                          "type": "null"
                        },
                        "amount": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "const": 1
                        },
                        "amount_approved": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "const": 1
                        },
                        "currency_id": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "const": 1
                        },
                        "status": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "approved"
                        },
                        "type": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "payment"
                        },
                        "payment_method_type": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "credit_card"
                        },
                        "payment_method_used": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "MASTERCARD 524931******0339"
                        },
                        "net_merchant_amount": {
                          "type": "number",
                          "const": 0.67
                        },
                        "created_at": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "2026-02-21T21:48:13.000000Z"
                        },
                        "processed_at": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "const": "2026-02-21T21:48:13.000000Z"
                        }
                      },
                      "required": [
                        "id",
                        "internal_reference",
                        "merchant_reference",
                        "amount",
                        "amount_approved",
                        "currency_id",
                        "status",
                        "type",
                        "payment_method_type",
                        "payment_method_used",
                        "net_merchant_amount",
